714
00:48:09,999 --> 00:48:11,023
Hayır.

715
00:48:11,200 --> 00:48:14,328
- Onu benden alamazsınız. Hayır.
- İşte burada.

716
00:48:15,070 --> 00:48:17,402
Ben Bebek Brent'im.

717
00:48:19,475 --> 00:48:22,273
- Üzerini giy.
- Yuh!

718
00:48:22,878 --> 00:48:25,244
Kimim ben?

719
00:48:27,016 --> 00:48:29,143
